propsSchema.description:
Metric card for dashboards. Shows a single large formatted value from SQL, $param substitution in value, or a static value.

## Example — SQL

```json
{
  "type": "metric",
  "props": {
    "sql": "SELECT COUNT(*) FROM {{my_udf}}",
    "label": "Total Records",
    "format": "compact"
  }
}
```

## Example — static / param

```json
{
  "type": "metric",
  "props": {
    "value": "$record_count",
    "label": "Records",
    "suffix": " rows",
    "format": "comma"
  }
}
```
